    <svcproc id="s08.4.2" graphiccount="0">
        <title>Exhaust Manifolds</title>
        <specpara>
            <caution>
                <para>To prevent engine damage, hand torque all nuts and bolts of the exhaust manifolds. The exhaust
                    manifold hardware has a special high-temperature coating which will be damaged by air tools.
                </para>
            </caution>
            <caution>
                <para>To prevent engine damage, do not reuse exhaust manifold bolts or stud bolts.</para>
            </caution>
        </specpara>
        <specpara>
            <note>
                <para>Do not apply anti-seize compound to threads.</para>
            </note>
        </specpara>
    </svcproc>
